metadata.name: Prelude #1
metadata.description: Step into a world of vibrant color and intricate patterns with our genesis collection. These digital artworks are generated by algorithm, resulting in unique and one-of-a-kind tessellation patterns that will delight and mesmerize. Each piece is a true treasure, waiting to be discovered and added to your collection. Immerse yourself in the beauty of these tessellated designs and add some color to your digital world. More to follow..
